summary: Taylor Swift Was Indisputably the Life of the Party at the TIME 100 Gala  TIME // by Ashley Hoffman // April 23rd 2019 If you...
body:
Taylor Swift Was Indisputably the Life of the Party at the TIME 100 Gala


TIME // by Ashley Hoffman // April 23rd 2019

If you weren’t already aware that Taylor Swift is one of the most social celebrities on Earth, then you perhaps haven’t caught her in action at a party. The Reputation singer was practically the social director at the 2019 TIME 100 Gala.

Before she took the stage to bring the house down with her performance, she worked the room full of her fellow honorees. There she was with a number of honorees like activists Sarah Leah Whitson and Radhya al-Mutawakel. And look, there she was bonding with the Game of Thrones star Emilia Clarke who knelt down to steal a chat.

And there she was chatting up soccer superstar Alex Morgan (“Dude, I’m so proud of you,” Swift enthused) and superhero, box office-buster Captain Marvelstar Brie Larson. And of course, she appeared to talk shop with fellow music industry dominator, Khalid who also performed for his fellow TIME 100 honorees.

See photos of Taylor Swift at the TIME 100 gala for proof.

summary: This woman means everything to me. Her performance and all of her speeches last night took my breath away. I’m privileged to get...
body:
This woman means everything to me. Her performance and all of her speeches last night took my breath away. I’m privileged to get the chance to support her and to play any part in her career at all: by buying her music and celebrating with her at concerts. I love you, Taylor Swift. I do. Thank you for everything 💖

And, oh yeah, I did cry during New Year’s Day…again. Incredible.

@taylorswift @taylornation
